{"tid":2112213,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"九月投票倒模王冬胜 - 陳也","createTime":"2020-07-17T06:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T06:47:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bfb976dfa74bce7c5c2b74bf1fce39081e871f52","tid":2112213,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T06:47:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200717/20957435/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200717%2F20957435%2F&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=164513ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200717%2F20957435%2F&h=cd914148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200717/20957435/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n九月投票倒模王冬胜 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200717/large/1594888296_02c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200717%2Flarge%2F1594888296_02c4.jpg&h=64bcf17e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民&times;聯晒冷見記者，拍照背景寫住「反攬炒，救香港」。但出師不利排位拍出來的照片，剛好遮住個「反」字，得返「攬炒救香港」。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。初選前，武肺忽然再爆發，源頭不明，疑點重重。時間卻是校到啱啱好，港府食住個勢借武肺翻發，人人自危，初選又冇錢賣頭版廣告，妄想有17萬票咁多？鄭市長摵起條眉冷笑：嘿你哋諗多咗！誰知，死啦&hellip;&hellip;好多票！蛇餅無齋，兼夾欠粽，照排你兩粒鐘！<br />\n<br />\n鄭氏攬炒，還有什麼板斧？DQ拉人告国安法嗎？香港人的恐懼已經由心落格到胃，消化咗。分化泛民與本土抗爭派嗎？兄弟爬山，各自開燈，初選結果連長期埋伏的攪屎棍都被迫收檔。保皇契弟。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}